# Parce

- Dev Build
- Local Server
- HMR - Hot Module Replacememt
- File Watching Algorithm - written in C++
- Caching - faster build
- Image Optimization
- Minification of code
- Bundling
- compression of file
- consistent hashing
- code splitting
- Differential Bundling - support older browser
- Diagnostic
- Error Handling
- https enabler is also in parcel
- zero config
- Tree shaking algorithm - remove unused code
- Different dev and prod bundles
